
## 6. Dependencies

Key libraries include:

*   Python 3.7 (as per `environment.yml`)
*   PyTorch (`torch`)
*   PyTorch Geometric (`torch_geometric`)
*   ESM (Facebook Research) (`fair-esm`)
*   Optuna
*   Pandas
*   NumPy
*   Scikit-learn (`sklearn`)
*   Matplotlib
*   SciPy
*   BioPython
*   tqdm
*   tensorboardX (or `torch.utils.tensorboard`)

All dependencies are listed in `environment.yml`. It's highly recommended to use this file to create the Conda environment.
